residential_units.tenure: Affordable Rent (not at LAR benchmark rents)

site_name: Development At Builders Yard And Land At
description: Redevelopment of site to provide 98 new affordable homes across three blocks (2x five storey and  1x 4 storey) with associated public realm improvements, landscaping, car parking, cycle and refuse/recycling storage and improvements to Station Approach.  (summary)
decision_conditions:
The short and long stay cycle parking serving the flats hereby approved hereby approved shall be installed as per the approved details prior to first occupation and retained, not used for any other purpose and be maintained in good working order for the lifetime of the development.

Reason: To ensure appropriate cycle storage is provided in the scheme to comply with policy T5 of the London Plan.
